{"tid":2331753,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"如果想直播有咩要求?","createTime":"2020-12-19T05:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T00:31:29.000Z","uid":36861,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b543fa22d38ab5006b87a680b4e813e5d7690781","tid":2331753,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"直播下教下AI Photoshop, 3D modeling, solidwork, zbrush, blender<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個D, 間唔中打下機<br />\n想有個chatroom, 之後播完會可以upload youtube 等人地睇返, 唔識editing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 係咪無得做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n有咩要買? 平平地幾千蚊得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我既諗法係:<br />\n買枝有毛毛既咪,<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買多個mon (宜家個個mon係27吋 LG ultrawide, 平時用黎畫野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 買多個放chatroom,同做主mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我呢個ultra wide用黎直出<br />\n<br />\n唔買cam, 因為我樣衰都無人會睇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買個4TB HD backup 自己既片 (1080)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平台係咪係youtube開個AC就得? 有無其他平台係好D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人睇, 所以無咩筆直, 上網睇教學又好似好多買要買咁, 我打算用返自己既keyboard同mouse. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外會買個gaming headset, 大約500-800 有無諗? 定係其實唔使買? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以比小小意見小弟, 利申宜家無返工。<br />\n<br />\n同如果直播, 大家多數會鐘意睇咩? 教學野係咪無人睇的?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外如果直播D software有license,係咪可以用教學版? 定要比錢買full? solidworks 好撚貴.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真問, 唔該各位大佬屌細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab57c997eab2bbb024a5663847bbe9dd9b5cb7e","tid":2331753,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得mic 好重要。之前自己用Mac book pro (2015, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未壞) 用QuickTime capture 個screen 講下 d it 野。 buildin mic 唔掂，就算買external 都收得一般，可能要用YouTuber 個d 電溶mic 先收得好。<br />\n<br />\nhard disk size 都好重要，下下幾十 GB 好快冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b914669bdfba45b8fb4ec7846464ce8890b9c99","tid":2331753,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab57c997eab2bbb024a5663847bbe9dd9b5cb7e","tid":2331753,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得mic 好重要。之前自己用Mac book pro (2015, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未壞) 用QuickTime capture 個screen 講下 d it 野。 buildin mic 唔掂，就算買external 都收得一般，可能要用YouTuber 個d 電溶mic 先收得好。<br />\n<br />\nhard disk size 都好重要，下下幾十 GB 好快冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"不過直播就唔關hard disk 事。"},{"pid":"176c6a5082c8590ff5da1179d182f9a4538e81e2","tid":2331753,"uid":36861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aab57c997eab2bbb024a5663847bbe9dd9b5cb7e","tid":2331753,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得mic 好重要。之前自己用Mac book pro (2015, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未壞) 用QuickTime capture 個screen 講下 d it 野。 buildin mic 唔掂，就算買external 都收得一般，可能要用YouTuber 個d 電溶mic 先收得好。<br />\n<br />\nhard disk size 都好重要，下下幾十 GB 好快冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"我用過耳機個咪, 收到屋企人洗碗同講野...聽人講買個好D既咪, 但唔知點...網上推個D又貴"},{"pid":"f4bce9cec287d8e452d141d55762955917b24525","tid":2331753,"uid":36861,"like":0,"d